---
title: Mexican Shrimp Tacos with Cabbage Carrot Slaw
description: Everyone loves taco night, and these are sure to satisfy your taco craving! Tender shrimp are flavoured with Mexican spices and quickly pan-fried to bring a savoury, tangy bite to the tacos. The super fresh slaw adds a layer of crunch, while the soft flour tortilla ties it all together in a single mouth-watering dish! Yum!
